        "html": "<p>Soit <span class=\"math inline\">\\(A \\in \\mathcal{M}_n(K)\\)</span>\ninversible et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(B = A^{-1}\\)</span>, <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(C = A^2\\)</span>. Exprimer les polynômes\ncaractéristiques <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\chi_B\\)</span> et <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(\\chi_C\\)</span> en fonction de <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(\\chi_A\\)</span>.</p>\n"
